POInterfaceLPL is a BusinessTask
    owned by po

    Parameters
        Company                 	is a PurchasingCompany
        DefaultBuyer				is a Buyer
        IncludeAllCostOptions		is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                Yes 				value is "Y"
                CostRequiredOnly  	value is "N"
        DefaultDeliveryDays			is Numeric size 3
        ReleasePurchaseOrder		is Boolean
        CombineOnPOLine             is Boolean
        OneShipToPerPO				is Boolean
        MaximumPOLines				is like Requisition
        ReportLevel             	is Numeric size 1
            States
                Detail 		value is 0
                Summary		value is 1
        PrintPOComments				is Boolean
        PrintByPOStatus				is Numeric size 1
            States
                All    		value is 0
                Unreleased 	value is 1
                Released	value is 2
        PrintExceptionReport		is Numeric size 1
            States
                DoNotPrintExceptionReport	value is 0
                    default label is "Do not print Exception Report"
                SortByVendorPurchFr			value is 1
                    default label is "Sort by Vendor/Purchase From"
                SortByItem					value is 2
                    default label is "Sort by Item"
                SortBySourceDocument		value is 3
                    default label is "Sort by Source Document"
                SortByBuyerCode				value is 4
                    default label is "Sort by Buyer Code"
        SystemCode              	is AlphaUpper size 2
            States
                InventoryControl  value is "IC"
                Requisitions      value is "RQ"
                OrderEntry        value is "OE"
                CaseCarts         value is "CX"
                StrategicSourcing value is "SS"
        VendorOption          		is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                Include 	value is "I"
                Exclude 	value is "E"
        Vendor						is a VendorArray
        FilterBuyer            		is a Buyer
        BuyerOnPurchasingClasses	is Boolean
        BuyerOnVendor				is Boolean
        BuyerOnLocation				is Boolean
        BuyerOnRequestingLocation	is Boolean
        FilterDeliveryDays			is Numeric size 3
        FilterFromPriority			is Numeric size 2
        FilterToPriority			is Numeric size 2
        FilterLocation				is an InventoryLocation
        FilterReportGroup			is an InventoryReportGroup
        POCodeOption				is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                Include 	value is "I"
                Exclude 	value is "E"
        FilterPOCode				is a POCodeArray
        FilterMajorPurchasingClass	is a MajorPurchasingClass
        FilterMinorPurchasingClass	is a MinorPurchasingClass
        FilterRequestingLocation	is a RequestingLocation
  		FilterItem					is an Item	
        FilterItemType				is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                Inventory 	value is "I"
                Nonstock  	value is "N"
                Special   	value is "X"
                Service   	value is "S"
        FilterManufacturerCode		is a Manufacturer
        FilterManufacturerDiv		is AlphaUpper size 4
        FilterRequistion			is Numeric size 7
        FilterProcurementTemplate	is Numeric size 8
        BillCodeOption				is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                Include 	value is "I"
                Exclude 	value is "E"
        FilterConsignCode			is a ConsignCodeArray
        FilterAccountingUnit		is an AccountingUnit
        FilterActivity				is a Project
        FilterCostCode				is a CostCode

    Parameter Rules
        Company
            required
        DefaultBuyer
            required
        IncludeAllCostOptions
        	initial value is "N"
            required
        DefaultDeliveryDays
            required
		FilterBuyer
			if (BuyerOnPurchasingClasses)
				required
					"MustEnterBuyerIfLimitingByBuyerClass"
			if (BuyerOnVendor)
				required
					"MustEnterBuyerIfLimitingByBuyerVendors"
			if (BuyerOnLocation)
				required
					"MustEnterBuyerIfLimitingByBuyerLocations"				
			if (BuyerOnRequestingLocation)
				required
					"MustEnterBuyerIfLimitingByBuyerRequestingLocations"
		FilterFromPriority
			if (FilterToPriority entered)
				required
					"MustEnterBothEndsOfThePriorityRange"
		FilterToPriority
			if (FilterFromPriority entered)
				required
					"MustEnterBothEndsOfThePriorityRange"












    Actions
        POInterface is an Instance Action

